Five.

83
00:04:35,568 --> 00:04:36,208
Four.

84
00:04:38,927 --> 00:04:39,888
Three.

85
00:04:41,747 --> 00:04:42,247
Two.

86
00:04:42,247 --> 00:04:43,328
Lu,

87
00:04:43,607 --> 00:04:44,487
