110
00:06:00,487 --> 00:06:01,968
Su Yunian, I'm begging you.

111
00:06:02,128 --> 00:06:03,568
Let's get out of here, okay?

112
00:06:05,727 --> 00:06:06,768
I'm not joking with you.

113
00:06:06,768 --> 00:06:07,847
It's very dangerous.

114
00:06:07,968 --> 00:06:08,768
I have my...

115
