135
00:06:52,328 --> 00:06:53,008
What should I do?

136
00:06:53,008 --> 00:06:53,568
Ruxue.

137
00:06:53,568 --> 00:06:54,208
Rose.

138
00:06:54,888 --> 00:06:55,727
Rose.

139
00:06:56,487 --> 00:06:57,128
Ms. Bai.

140
00:06:58,008 --> 00:06:58,648
Ms. Bai.

141
00:06:58,648 --> 00:06:59,487
What is it?

142
00:07:00,208 --> 00:07:02,047
Director Smir of the Intelligence Bureau

143
00:07:02,528 --> 00:07:03,727
