150
00:07:15,727 --> 00:07:17,088
She was just joking with me.

151
00:07:17,088 --> 00:07:17,648
Later,

152
00:07:17,648 --> 00:07:18,807
I'll set her straight.

153
00:07:18,948 --> 00:07:19,448
I promise

154
00:07:19,448 --> 00:07:20,328
- she won't...
- Ruxue,

155
00:07:21,247 --> 00:07:22,528
gather at Room 666 later

156
00:07:23,167 --> 00:07:24,727
