163
00:07:35,927 --> 00:07:36,727
(Room 666.)

164
00:07:39,727 --> 00:07:40,528
(Three days after An Ruoxi's murder)
Ruoxi,

165
00:07:40,888 --> 00:07:41,648
tell me

166
00:07:42,128 --> 00:07:43,448
