167
00:07:49,088 --> 00:07:49,847
Who is it?

168
00:08:37,376 --> 00:08:39,808
(Deep in the Bustle)

169
00:08:40,727 --> 00:08:42,367
Deep in the Bustle.

170
00:08:45,312 --> 00:08:49,962
(Ruoxi was killed.)

171
00:08:49,962 --> 00:08:52,864
(Avenge her.)

172
00:08:53,127 --> 00:08:55,247
(If this really is Ruoxi's bracelet,)

173
00:08:55,647 --> 00:08:57,688
(it should help me)

174
00:08:58,127 --> 00:08:59,887
(take the Tian elevator)

175
00:09:00,328 --> 00:09:01,647
(and enter Room 666 smoothly.)

176
00:09:02,328 --> 00:09:03,527
(Seizing this chance,)

177
00:09:03,808 --> 00:09:05,448
(I might test its authenticity.)

178
00:09:15,727 --> 00:09:16,808
(It works perfectly.)

179
00:09:51,647 --> 00:09:52,688
(Hiding here)

180
00:09:53,007 --> 00:09:53,808
(should be okay.)

181
00:09:54,048 --> 00:09:55,127
(If I'm discovered,)

182
00:09:55,527 --> 00:09:57,928
(I'll say I came up to deliver supplies)

183
00:09:58,088 --> 00:09:59,168
(and got the wrong room.)

184
00:10:12,576 --> 00:10:13,679
Another meeting.

185
00:10:15,088 --> 00:10:16,767
Every exhausting day.

186
00:10:17,247 --> 00:10:19,088
Yours has good quality.

187
00:10:19,088 --> 00:10:19,727
Pretty, right?

188
00:10:19,727 --> 00:10:21,088
Pretty. Acceptable.

189
00:10:24,767 --> 00:10:25,968
- Ms. Bai!
- Hello, Ms. Bai.

190
00:10:25,968 --> 00:10:26,767
Hello, Ms. Bai.

191
00:10:27,727 --> 00:10:28,367
Sit.

192
00:10:31,887 --> 00:10:33,048
Two things today.

193
00:10:33,487 --> 00:10:35,887
The performance summary
for the first half of the month.

194
00:10:37,247 --> 00:10:38,288
And

195
00:10:38,408 --> 00:10:39,847
