199
00:10:53,408 --> 00:10:54,208
What else?

200
00:10:56,847 --> 00:10:57,527
Rose,

201
00:10:57,847 --> 00:10:58,607
what do you say?

202
00:10:59,727 --> 00:11:00,408
Right,

203
00:11:00,647 --> 00:11:01,847
she went abroad.

204
00:11:02,208 --> 00:11:03,808
I know that wealthy businessman.

205
00:11:03,808 --> 00:11:05,487
He visited our place a few times,

206
00:11:05,487 --> 00:11:06,727
always looking for Yunyan.

207
00:11:07,048 --> 00:11:09,487
Probably became his concubine.

208
00:11:10,088 --> 00:11:11,127
That can't be.

209
00:11:11,127 --> 00:11:13,647
- Exactly.
- Yunyan wasn't like that at all.

210
00:11:13,647 --> 00:11:14,928
Impossible!

211
00:11:14,928 --> 00:11:16,448
How could she go?

212
00:11:16,448 --> 00:11:17,344
How could this happen?

213
00:11:17,344 --> 00:11:17,952
Enough.

214
00:11:17,952 --> 00:11:19,168
Stop gossiping, everyone.

215
00:11:19,527 --> 00:11:21,647
Everyone has the right
to choose their own path.

216
00:11:23,247 --> 00:11:23,968
Ms. Bai,

217
00:11:23,968 --> 00:11:25,088
let me report first.

218
00:11:25,408 --> 00:11:26,007
Go ahead.

219
00:11:28,527 --> 00:11:30,288
This month's revenue on my end

220
00:11:30,288 --> 00:11:31,808
totals 8.92 million yuan,

221
00:11:32,328 --> 00:11:35,208
including 3 million
from the Pingliang State Culture Bureau

222
00:11:35,208 --> 00:11:36,384
deputy director's promotion.

223
00:11:36,384 --> 00:11:37,887
The remaining revenue comes from

224
00:11:37,968 --> 00:11:39,767
paying the Chief Justice of Lvteng City

225
00:11:39,767 --> 00:11:42,048
to overturn a 20-year sentence
to not guilty,

226
00:11:42,607 --> 00:11:44,688
promoting three civilian roles
in the Royal Forces,

227
00:11:44,688 --> 00:11:45,632
and processing two

228
00:11:45,632 --> 00:11:47,264
academy graduates into the police force.

229
00:11:48,127 --> 00:11:48,647
That's it.

230
00:11:49,048 --> 00:11:49,607
Additionally,

231
00:11:49,607 --> 00:11:50,847
regarding the Laurences,

232
00:11:50,847 --> 00:11:52,247
I've secured the partnership.

233
00:11:52,328 --> 00:11:54,208
Girls, please don't interfere for now.

234
00:11:54,208 --> 00:11:54,887
Sorry, Ruxue,

235
00:11:54,887 --> 00:11:55,808
