by Yunyan with us.

239
00:12:00,408 --> 00:12:01,088
Ruxue,

240
00:12:01,247 --> 00:12:02,487
now that Yunyan's gone,

241
00:12:02,767 --> 00:12:04,568
are you trying to monopolize this?

242
00:12:04,688 --> 00:12:05,647
Exactly!

243
00:12:05,647 --> 00:12:08,168
Last time the Laurences visited,

244
00:12:08,168 --> 00:12:09,928
we hosted them together.

245
00:12:10,088 --> 00:12:12,367
Why is it your exclusive deal?

246
00:12:12,727 --> 00:12:13,568
Ms. Bai,

247
00:12:13,568 --> 00:12:15,968
when the Laurences first came,

248
00:12:15,968 --> 00:12:16,968
we were all present.

249
00:12:16,968 --> 00:12:17,647
Right?

250
00:12:18,767 --> 00:12:19,887
Please judge this fairly.

251
00:12:20,408 --> 00:12:21,527
How did it end up

252
00:12:21,968 --> 00:12:23,408
being solely Ruxue's deal?

253
00:12:24,887 --> 00:12:25,647
Girls,

254
00:12:25,647 --> 00:12:26,727
let me explain.

255
00:12:27,247 --> 00:12:29,527
The party's uncle

256
00:12:29,527 --> 00:12:31,007
was Yunyan's client.

257
00:12:31,247 --> 00:12:33,088
Yunyan approached Ruxue

258
00:12:33,328 --> 00:12:34,968
for the Chief Justice's connection.

259
00:12:35,247 --> 00:12:37,527
Logically, it belongs to Ruxue.

260
00:12:37,568 --> 00:12:39,367
Not your place to speak.

261
00:12:39,647 --> 00:12:41,647
We agree to divide among the Tian Class.

262
00:12:41,928 --> 00:12:43,568
Why are you, a Yun Class girl, here?

263
00:12:43,568 --> 00:12:44,688
All of you, silence!

264
00:12:46,408 --> 00:12:47,727
The Laurences

265
00:12:47,808 --> 00:12:49,408
isn't subject to monopolization.

266
00:12:50,127 --> 00:12:51,088
Is that clear?

267
00:12:51,247 --> 00:12:52,408
- Understood.
- Understood.

268
00:12:54,767 --> 00:12:55,408
Furthermore,

269
00:12:55,767 --> 00:12:56,928
let me reiterate.

270
00:12:57,928 --> 00:12:59,487
At Deep In The Bustle,

271
00:13:00,408 --> 00:13:02,367
whoever secures top-tier resources

272
00:13:02,647 --> 00:13:04,367
