275
00:13:09,527 --> 00:13:11,208
so the commission goes to her.

276
00:13:12,328 --> 00:13:13,847
What she shares with you

277
00:13:14,048 --> 00:13:15,168
is your private arrangement.

278
00:13:15,688 --> 00:13:17,048
Set terms upfront.

279
00:13:17,328 --> 00:13:18,767
Avoid disputes later.

280
00:13:19,887 --> 00:13:20,527
Understood?

281
00:13:21,968 --> 00:13:22,568
Also,

282
00:13:23,448 --> 00:13:24,767
strive for fairness.

283
00:13:25,168 --> 00:13:26,647
Don't make them resentful.

284
00:13:27,247 --> 00:13:27,887
Yes, Ms. Bai.

285
00:13:29,968 --> 00:13:30,767
Next.

286
00:13:46,688 --> 00:13:48,168
Why is Su Yunian there?

287
