Just as I thought.

291
00:14:13,288 --> 00:14:15,007
Proceed with this distribution plan.

292
00:14:15,328 --> 00:14:16,007
Three days.

293
00:14:17,088 --> 00:14:18,328
Within three days,

294
00:14:18,688 --> 00:14:20,208
no matter the means,

295
00:14:20,647 --> 00:14:22,127
you must invite

296
00:14:22,127 --> 00:14:23,127
all your contacts

297
00:14:23,168 --> 00:14:24,048
and coordinate.

298
00:14:24,367 --> 00:14:25,007
Remember,

299
00:14:25,767 --> 00:14:27,208
no slip-ups allowed.

300
00:14:27,688 --> 00:14:28,527
It must be ours.

301
00:14:29,288 --> 00:14:30,247
- I see.
- I see.

302
00:14:30,247 --> 00:14:31,448
Understood, Ms. Bai.

303
00:14:33,527 --> 00:14:34,328
Ms. Bai,

304
00:14:35,168 --> 00:14:36,688
could I have the deputy governor

305
00:14:36,928 --> 00:14:38,048
Yunyan handled?

306
00:14:38,408 --> 00:14:39,328
I entertained him.

307
00:14:39,328 --> 00:14:40,448
He seemed quite fond of me.

308
00:14:40,568 --> 00:14:42,688
I don't have
any state-level projects now.

309
00:14:43,367 --> 00:14:44,527
I've spent time with him.

310
00:14:44,767 --> 00:14:46,208
He even asked me to marry him.

311
00:14:46,688 --> 00:14:48,208
You actually believe

312
00:14:48,208 --> 00:14:48,808
their words?

313
00:14:48,808 --> 00:14:49,448
Alright.

314
00:14:49,448 --> 00:14:50,088
Be quiet!

315
00:14:51,208 --> 00:14:52,288
Let's call it a day.

316
00:14:52,487 --> 00:14:53,048
Dismissed.

317
00:14:53,487 --> 00:14:54,168
Sill have guests.

318
00:14:54,168 --> 00:14:54,968
Get back to work.

319
00:14:56,367 --> 00:14:57,527
Ms. Bai, you leaving?

320
00:14:57,647 --> 00:14:58,568
Go ahead.

321
00:14:58,647 --> 00:15:00,208
I need to organize these reports

322
00:15:00,208 --> 00:15:01,288
and send them to Mr. Tu.

323
00:15:01,847 --> 00:15:03,328
Mr. Nie is waiting for my report.

324
00:15:03,527 --> 00:15:04,367
You go first.

325
00:15:04,448 --> 00:15:05,808
Close the door when you leave.

326
00:15:07,688 --> 00:15:08,188
Ms. Bai,

327
00:15:08,408 --> 00:15:10,048
this is the rose tea I brewed for you.

328
00:15:10,168 --> 00:15:11,048
Good for skincare.

329
00:15:11,208 --> 00:15:12,007
Have it warm.

330
00:15:12,007 --> 00:15:12,767
Thanks.

331
00:15:15,688 --> 00:15:16,727
I'll head out first then.

332
00:15:16,808 --> 00:15:17,308
Okay.

333
00:15:22,208 --> 00:15:23,168
Hello, Mr. Tu.

334
00:15:26,767 --> 00:15:27,288
Okay.

335
00:15:28,168 --> 00:15:28,887
I see.

336
00:15:45,847 --> 00:15:46,527
Ms. Bai.

337
00:15:47,767 --> 00:15:48,607
Why are you here?

338
00:15:50,168 --> 00:15:52,168
I-I came to clean up in advance.

339
00:16:00,328 --> 00:16:00,928
Let's go.

340
00:16:01,247 --> 00:16:02,240
Mr. Tu wants to see you.

341
00:16:02,928 --> 00:16:03,527
Mr. Tu

342
00:16:03,968 --> 00:16:04,767
wants to see me?

343
00:16:26,887 --> 00:16:28,448
(If he saw from the camera)

344
00:16:28,688 --> 00:16:30,168
(that I use Ruoxi's bracelet)

345
00:16:30,168 --> 00:16:31,088
(to open the door,)

346
00:16:31,487 --> 00:16:32,808
(I have no choice but to admit)

347
00:16:32,808 --> 00:16:34,168
(I'm her sister.)

348
00:16:34,727 --> 00:16:36,688
(If he didn't see that,)

349
00:16:37,127 --> 00:16:37,767
(maybe)

350
00:16:38,247 --> 00:16:39,688
(I have a chance to hide it.)

351
00:16:40,408 --> 00:16:41,127
(Forget it.)

352
00:16:41,688 --> 00:16:43,007
(I'll have to face it one day.)

353
00:16:43,688 --> 00:16:44,188
(Ruoxi,)

354
00:16:44,647 --> 00:16:45,487
(with you here,)

355
00:16:46,048 --> 00:16:46,767
(I'm not afraid.)

356
00:17:02,592 --> 00:17:06,266
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

357
00:17:06,565 --> 00:17:09,756
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

358
00:17:11,424 --> 00:17:15,209
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

359
00:17:15,758 --> 00:17:18,816
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

360
00:17:20,028 --> 00:17:23,758
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

361
00:17:23,982 --> 00:17:27,552
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

362
00:17:28,878 --> 00:17:32,565
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

363
00:17:33,203 --> 00:17:38,318
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

364
00:17:39,022 --> 00:17:43,156
♪I feel guilty♪

365
00:17:43,726 --> 00:17:47,470
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

366
00:17:48,334 --> 00:17:51,777
♪Even in tears♪

367
00:17:52,526 --> 00:17:56,440
♪It doesn't matter♪

368
00:17:56,622 --> 00:18:00,445
♪We embrace in dreams♪

369
00:18:01,294 --> 00:18:04,732
♪I let down all my defenses♪

370
00:18:05,966 --> 00:18:09,329
♪Though the story has its end♪

371
00:18:10,094 --> 00:18:17,504
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
